MasterChef South Africa - Season 3, Episode 2




Final Battle for Top 12

With only 24 contestants surviving the first day of Boot Camp in Cape Town harbour, the stakes were high on MasterChef South Africa tonight as they faced an Invention test with a mystery ingredient halfway to the challenge for a place in the MasterChef kitchen in Paarl.




Original Air Date: 28-Aug-2014
